please help me because im quite a noob when it comes to problems i have searched forums for help but cant find it so please dont tell me too

item.title: Java noob help needed
item.dc:creator: @Iamadam Iamadam
item.description:
@Iamadam wrote:

Make sure you compile the classes (Compile-Classes.bat)
If there is an error with that, open up accessor methods (in the botclasses folder) and find ‘anInt950’. Replace that with rs.anInt950
Then click compile classes again.
